{"tid":2399470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"fitness panda買嘢 遲遲唔出貨 有無一樣苦主","createTime":"2021-02-08T07:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T07:03:46.000Z","uid":38165,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"455b317cf8809aa4ae458ab3efb4a058f5b28ff3","tid":2399470,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"細佬係上月24號 即係1月24日 <br />\n經網上去fitness panda買左款運動口罩 <br />\n連埋運費就170幾蚊<br />\n<br />\n咁我買完就等收貨<br />\n而佢個網站個頂部就寫住<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwYxb8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwYxb8o.png&h=86bd883d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現貨就1-3日出貨 咁無現貨果啲就要7-14日訂完再出貨啦<br />\n咁好正常 依家武肺緊 送貨耐啲好閒<br />\n<br />\n我買果款口罩就寫明有現貨嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmEo3fQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmEo3fQ.png&h=acafbbdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我比完錢之後過左9日 禮拜六日唔開<br />\n咁當佢過左7日工作天 件貨仍然無消息 <br />\n跟住我whatsapp佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好屌用whatsapp住<br />\n佢依間嘢得whatsapp 同電話聯絡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rkSWCn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rkSWCn.png&h=987752e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我已經好聲好氣咁問佢幾時會出貨等等 <br />\n但雙tick仲要一直唔覆<br />\n<br />\n跟住我今日打電話過去 ：電話暫時未能接通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知依間鋪係咪執左定無人打理 <br />\n但最起馬應該要有個交待<br />\n搞到我唔知仲出唔出去買過另外一個好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊幾水預左無 想睇下有無一樣苦主"},{"pid":"60b394a164eda596819f3198b5d1811c34d2a223","tid":2399470,"uid":70439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"當跌咗啦，呢間呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb154adc497332c60fc1f4600f0ded92fa9af2c","tid":2399470,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"8a1a45703af92125763d4fe998760c800a55b38b","tid":2399470,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"我哥哥試過E間<br />\n<br />\n送錯ge貨品比佢，唔肯退錢<br />\n<br />\n勸大家唔好再試"},{"pid":"2fc435df53f597db9ca64c89c66bceeb7c4d9592","tid":2399470,"uid":340192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"幫你推下，屌你老味咁做生意都得"},{"pid":"44ab809d8289f355dc86bec8c91a8039ae25c143","tid":2399470,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"支持樓主！垃圾店就要俾大家知！"},{"pid":"5c532e5df508c73afad94d86a891dda80077e9db","tid":2399470,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"f3c522bd4ea0c3f022ca044ab9e2e18b08ce15fd","tid":2399470,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5c74009b70e40e7204c5b83aa823e0cea6560d3d","tid":2399470,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60b394a164eda596819f3198b5d1811c34d2a223","tid":2399470,"uid":70439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:20:05.000Z","msg":"當跌咗啦，呢間呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:13:04.000Z","msg":"係呀 舊幾水豪比狗 <br />\n但想大家知道依間黑店！"},{"pid":"3a007a6d8d142ef9ffab850b9068fe14e2629e7b","tid":2399470,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:13:41.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c54a76e1c5117e837a662f4b51bd2f49bc9af45c","tid":2399470,"uid":38165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a1a45703af92125763d4fe998760c800a55b38b","tid":2399470,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"我哥哥試過E間<br />\n<br />\n送錯ge貨品比佢，唔肯退錢<br />\n<br />\n勸大家唔好再試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" clas